etter xp, 1 Plat (the first time anyway) and better armor (which if you don't need you can sell for at least 8g)<br><br>After you've played your Warrior for a while and you want to start a new one. then concider the choices above.<br>If you want the stongest go for an Ogre<br>If you want to have a lot of fun and be different pick a Gnome. (this is a cool race becase you can go to any city and not be KOS) ((all but Iskar of course))</p></td></td></tr><tr><td colspan="2" class="mform2"><table border=0 cellspacing=0 cellpadding=0 width="100%"><tr><td id=fs8></td><td align=right id=fs8 >0 Replies</td></tr></table></td></tr></table><tr><td class=mhback align=right><span class=mh id=fs8><a class=mh href=/db/classes.html?class=1><img src=/shared/root_thread_ico.gif border=0 alt="Up" width=17 height=11> Thread Index</a> |  <a class=mh href=/db/classes.html?class=1&post=1><img src=/shared/new_thread_ico.gif border=0 alt="New" width=17 height=11> New Subject</a> | <a class=mh href=/db/classes.html?class=1&mid=96682750913062&num=9&page=&post=1&mid=96682750913062><img src=/shared/reply_to_thread_ico.gif border=0 alt="Reply" width=17 height=11> Reply to Thread</a></span></td></tr><tr><td><table width="100%" border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" class="mform"><tr><td id="fs8">9 Posts [ <a href="/fsearch.html?base=class1">Search Forums</a> ]</nobr></td></tr></table>&nbsp;</td></tr>
